; Cross-unit fixture for assoc-types A4.3 (.nuch round-trip of a &where extend).
;
; After A4.4: MapIter, UnaryFn, and the &where extend are now part of
; lib/iterator.nuc. This fixture re-exports them through the .nuch import path,
; testing that the TmplConformance (and its &where clause) survives --emit-nuch
; round-trip and allows stamp-time recovery in the importing unit.
;
; Regenerate the header with:
;     nucleusc --emit-nuch tests/fixtures/mapiterlib.nuc > lib/mapiterlib.nuch

(import-use iterator)
